                     <hi rend="largeCaps">DAVID MURPHY</hi> (28)</persName>
                  <rs id="t18750503-304-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18750503-304-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18750503-304-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="embezzlement"></interp>, Unlawfully conspiring to incite <persName id="t18750503-name-19" type="victimName">
