                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18750503-304-offence-1 t18750503-name-19"></join>Herbert Cornish Poole</persName> to embezzle and steal monies of the <persName id="t18750503-name-20" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18750503-name-20" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18750503-304-offence-1 t18750503-name-20"></join>London General Omnibus Company (Limited)</persName>.</rs>
